IncidentSuppNarrative.NarrativeText: On Monday, February 20, 2023 at approximately 1014 hours, I, Trooper First Class Hunt 6939, responded to the Maryland State Police Princess Anne Barrack and made contact with a female subject and her daughter in the front lobby, who wanted to file a report of an adult male sending inappropriate messages to the daughter via Snapchat. The mother was identified by her Maryland Drivers License as, Laura Nicole Williams (DOB: 04/11/1985, 5/F), and the juvenile was identified as, Jadyn Alise Williams (DOB:12/13/2008, 1/F). I asked Laura what had happened and she stated, A grown man was sending her inappropriate messages and sent a picture of his gentiles. Laura then pointed to her daughter and Jayden proceeded to read the messages (messages via Instagram and Snapchat attached to the report for reference). I asked Jadyn who the man was and she stated, His name is Khai he used to work at my school, Somerset Intermediate. I then asked Jadyn how this all started and she stated, He followed me on Instagram and asked me to add him on Snapchat and I did. Laura then stated, I told her when he started sending some of the questionable messages to keep talking to him and we will see if he does anything he should. While messaging with Khai on Snapchat, Khai sent a photo and deleted it prior to Jadyn being able to view the photo. Jadyn asked Khai what the message was that he had deleted to which he stated, O my fat dick. Jadyn stated, u sent me it? Khai then stated, Yea my fault. I asked Jadyn if she was ever able to see the photo that Khai had sent and she stated, No he deleted it. I asked Jadyn when the last time that she had contacted Khai to which she stated, January 26 but then he deleted me. I asked if she knew Khais last name and she stated, No but he lives down in Marion. I asked Jadyn if she had Khais phone number to which she stated, No, but he has been messaging my friend too. I then asked Jadyn if she knew how many people he was messaging like this and she stated, No but its a few. Khai was later identified as, Khai Nathaniel Sterling (DOB:10/10/2002, H/M). Contact was not made with Khai in regards to this incident. Laura and Jadyn both completed written statements in regards to this incident and both have been attached to the report for reference. I request that this case be forwarded to CED for further investigation.

Based on a separate investigation (23-MSP-020379), a subpoena was served on Snap chat for subscriber information of Draco_boygang. Upon return the following information was provided ( A copy of the Snap chat response is attached to the case file): Email address khaisterling10@gmail.com margin-left:8px">Backup phone number (443) 953-1187. A search of Khai Sterling revealed a date of birth as 10/10/2002 with an address of 28464 Hudson Corner Road, Marion Station, Maryland. On October 10, 2023, Detective Schultz from the Wicomico County Child Advocacy Center and I responded to 28464 Hudson Corner Road, Marion Station, Maryland and made contact with Khai Sterling [hereinafter referred to as Sterling] Sterling was advised that our encounter was being audibly and visually recorded on body camera and that he was free to go and did not have to speak with investigators. Sterling agreed to speak with investigators, below is a synopsis of the interview and not a direct transcript therefore paraphrasing may be utilized: Sterling acknowledged that today was his birthday He agreed his Snap chat name was previously draco_boygang He agreed he previously worked at Somerset Intermediate School He denied sending pictures to students He denied any knowledge of the picture or comment my big fat dick He again confirmed the Draco_boygang was his snap chat margin-left:8px">Interview concluded Based on the age parameters of Sterling being more than 4 years older than Jadyn and the continuing course of conduct, investigators contacted the Somerset County Deputy States Attorney Hayward and decided charges would be filed. On October 11, 2023, I applied for and obtained an arrest warrant for Khai Sterling. At approximately 1645hrs, TFC Wilson and I responded to 28464 Hudson Corner Road and made contact with Sterling. Upon contact with Sterling, he was initially confrontational but with the assistance of Sterlings mother and de-escalation techniques Sterling was placed under arrest without incident. Sterling was transported to the Maryland State Police Princess Anne Barrack for processing. Upon arrival at the barrack Sterling was seated in the processing room. As I was filling out the warrant information, Sterling asked me to explain to him what was going on, prior to going over the warrant. I explained to Sterling that I wanted to make sure he understood his rights prior to me asking any questions, I read Sterling his Miranda Rights from an MSP 180 and Sterling agreed and signed the form. Below is a synopsis of the interview and not a direct transcript therefore paraphrasing may be utilized: Sterling signed an MSP 180 He identified Draco_boygang as a previous snap-chat username he used I began explaining the case regarding Jadyn He explained these girls just want his money I have hos I dont need her He identified his Instagram username saying thats me He agreed he added Jadyn on Snap chat and asked her to add back He identified his previous phone number He identified the email address Snap chat provided was his He agreed the Instagram username was his He explained Jadyn sent him a picture of her ass and asked him to rate it margin-bottom:11px">He agreed by saying facts that it is inappropriate to request explicit photos from underage girls A virtual hearing was conducted with the Somerset County District Court Commissioners Office via phone. Sterling was held without bond and transported to the Somerset County Detention Center without incident. Case Closed.
